[This mosquito-borne virus is no respecter of boundaries and has been found as far north as in Canada. It is very sad that owners still cannot learn to vaccinate to prevent deaths from EEE.

Vermont can be located on the interactive HealthMap at: http://healthmap.org/r/2XCM. - Mod.TG]
